(222, 114, 'Matt M', 'Matt@dlzip.com', 'http://www.MattMatteson.com', '138.67.141.10', '2008-08-27 11:12:38', '2008-08-27 18:12:38', 'Try the basics. No big meal before bed, stay away from glowing screens, no caffeine. I''ve also heard to only sleep in bed, don''t read or compute or watch TV or listen to radio, as your body can tie the simple fact that you go to this bed to sleep. Get some exercise in, perhaps you can just jog home or something so you don''t have to find more time in your day.\r\n\r\nJust some ideas, I hope things get better.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10_5_4; en-us) AppleWebKit/526.11 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0dp1 Safari/526.11.2', '', 0, 0, ''),
(223, 115, 'Josh', 'jlee1232@hotmail.com', 'http://popwrex.livejournal.com', '69.21.134.12', '2008-08-28 07:39:34', '2008-08-28 14:39:34', 'Huzzah, just remember to not show any one the soles of your feet or pick anything up with your left hand and they probably won''t kill you. Probably. Say hi to Elizabeth and Wes for Kara and I.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 7.0; Windows NT 5.1; .NET CLR 1.0.3705; .NET CLR 1.1.4322; Media Center PC 4.0)', '', 0, 0, ''),
