(245, 161, 'Andrew Ferguson', 'andrew@fergcorp.com', 'http://andrewferguson.net', '138.67.140.184', '2008-11-19 18:03:30', '2008-11-20 01:03:30', 'I picked up and read "Surely You’re Joking, Mr. Feynman!" just about two years ago (http://andrewferguson.net/2006/12/12/surely-youre-joking/) and I agree that it is an amazing book. I really wish I could have met him.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-US) AppleWebKit/525.19 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/0.3.154.9 Safari/525.19', '', 0, 0, ''),
