(257, 115, 'Shammi', 'shammisanawar@hotmail.com', '', '86.41.204.217', '2008-12-23 19:55:56', '2008-12-24 02:55:56', 'Hello Sir\r\n\r\nCongratulations for making it to the finals!\r\n\r\nHow did the interview go?\r\n\r\nlol i had an interview last week with Roche Pharmaceuticals and it was sooooo weird! They asked me weird questions that I wasn''t expecting!\r\n\r\nWhat did the KAUST people ask you?\r\n\r\nWould love to know!\r\n\r\nRegards\r\n\r\nShammi', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 6.0; en-GB; rv:1.9.0.5) Gecko/2008120122 Firefox/3.0.5', '', 0, 0, ''),
