(336, 115, 'waiting', 'rxfaith@gmail.com', '', '213.189.94.125', '2009-05-17 00:31:18', '2009-05-17 07:31:18', 'Any word yet?  Waiting is not fun at this point, since it is now May - decisions need to be made to other institutes.  Does anyone have any idea of who should be contacted?', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-US; rv:1.9.0.8) Gecko/2009032608 Firefox/3.0.8', '', 0, 0, ''),
(338, 115, 'Felipe', 'chillibogosian@gmail.com', '', '94.237.119.110', '2009-05-18 18:34:40', '2009-05-19 01:34:40', 'I had a phone interview and then I was contacted to have an interview in Dubai, however one week ago I was informed that the interviews were going to be postponed for several undisclosed reasons until further notice. However I am not applying for a student position but for a non-academic job.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; U; Intel Mac OS X 10.5; en-GB; rv:1.9.0.10) Gecko/2009042315 Firefox/3.0.10', '', 0, 0, ''),
