(2212, 898, 'tinku', 'tinkuminku123@gmail.com', '', '14.139.128.12', '2012-05-30 10:08:04', '2012-05-30 17:08:04', 'Thanks for the article!\r\n\r\nOne correction: \r\nint barDatatype; should be MPI_Datatype barDatatype;', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64) AppleWebKit/534.30 (KHTML, like Gecko) Ubuntu/10.10 Chromium/12.0.742.112 Chrome/12.0.742.112 Safari/534.30', '', 0, 0, ''),
(2201, 1061, 'dan.lecocq', 'dan.lecocq@kaust.edu.sa', 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress', '70.99.250.82', '2012-05-18 16:14:43', '2012-05-18 23:14:43', 'Thanks! It''s funny that you should leave that comment today, just as I was preparing a blog post on the the <a href="http://devblog.seomoz.org/2012/05/introducing-qless-our-new-job-queue/" rel="nofollow">project</a>.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_7_2) AppleWebKit/535.19 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/18.0.1025.168 Safari/535.19', '', 2200, 2, ''),
(2202, 1064, 'Josh', 'joshbob@gmail.com', '', '24.91.129.242', '2012-05-19 05:46:39', '2012-05-19 12:46:39', 'Hey Dan -\r\n\r\nYou might want to be careful using that name for the queuing system. There''s a company going by the same name (they do waiting lists for people), and I''m not sure how litigious they''re going to be feeling after getting sued by a competitor.\r\n\r\n - J', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/535.19 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/18.0.1025.168 Safari/535.19', '', 0, 0, ''),
(2096, 1007, 'Toby Champion', 'toby@tobychampion.com', '', '24.19.102.77', '2012-03-08 23:04:50', '2012-03-09 06:04:50', 'Dan,\r\n\r\nI just wrote a comment on http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=3683014 then tracked you down and realized you''re in Seattle. Small world, so, what''s up with Shovel? What didn''t you like about Fabric? Maybe write something on that page. I use Fabric every day, see.\r\n\r\nToby, Poulsbo (near Bainbridge Island) and SeaPIG.', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10.7; rv:10.0.2) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/10.0.2', '', 0, 0, ''),
(2100, 740, 'movers los angeles', 'Milanesi@gmail.com', 'http://maxmovers.co.il/', '114.34.174.124', '2012-03-12 02:17:08', '2012-03-12 09:17:08', 'I wanted to thank you again for the amazing site you have made here. It is full of ideas for those who are truly interested in this specific subject, especially this very post. You really are all so sweet and thoughtful of others and reading your site posts is an excellent delight to me. And exactly what a generous treat! Dan and I really have pleasure making use of your guidelines in what we need to do in the near future. Our record is a mile long which means your tips will be put to great use.', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.1; en-US; rv:1.9.0.14) Gecko/2009082707 Firefox/3.0.14 (.NET CLR 3.5.30729)', '', 0, 0, ''),
