(273, 1, '2008-12-04 11:48:13', '2008-12-04 18:48:13', 'There''s a guy who''s perpetually in alamode (the lab of choice for the C.S. major of discerning taste) named Feineman.  It was through him that I found <a href="http://failblog.org/">failblog</a> - he was tearing through the archive and it had some pretty funny stuff.\r\n\r\nYesterday he found yet another gem.  Apparently there''s a mutex (mutual exclusion) on sex and studying engineering:\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="aligncenter" width="400" caption="It&#39;s my future! I want to be an engineer... sex can wait!"]<a href="http://secretgeek.net/image/future.jpg"><img alt="Its my future! I want to be an engineer... sex can wait!" src="http://secretgeek.net/image/future.jpg" title="Sex Can Wait!" width="400"/></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\n', 'Sex and Engineering', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '204-revision-6', '', '', '2008-12-04 11:48:13', '2008-12-04 18:48:13', '', 204, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2008/12/04/204-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
