p, and for reading this all, here are some pictures:<br /><br /><div style="text-align:center;width:194px;font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:83%"><div style="height:194px;background:url(http://picasaweb.google.com/f/img/transparent_album_background.gif) no-repeat left"><a href="http://picasaweb.google.com/sowiebinich/fAheZD"><img src="http://lh6.google.com/image/sowiebinich/RdQNaWj95DE/AAAAAAAAAFw/3-CVcxA54RM/s160-c/fAheZD.jpg" width="160" height="160" style="border:none;padding:0px;margin-top:16px;"/></a></div><a href="http://picasaweb.google.com/sowiebinich/fAheZD"><div style="color:#4D4D4D;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;">札幌</div></a><div style="color:#808080"></div></div>', '札幌 Sapporo', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '82-revision-2', '', '', '2009-02-08 22:55:46', '2009-02-09 05:55:46', '', 82, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2009/02/08/82-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
