(453, 1, '2009-02-21 16:58:07', '2009-02-21 23:58:07', 'I made a lamp this weekend for Rachel as a belated Valentine''s Day gift.  Made from balsa wood, vellum, hot glue and the electrical components, I got my inspiration from <a href="http://www.instructables.com/id/5-Japanese-lamp-from-recycled-materials/">Instructables</a>.  It didn''t look well put-together, and so I made my own interpretation:\r\n\r\n[gallery link="file" orderby="ID"]\r\n\r\n', 'Lamp', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lamp', '', '', '2009-02-21 16:58:07', '2009-02-21 23:58:07', '', 0, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/?p=453', 0, 'post', '', 2),
