(472, 1, '2009-03-06 20:03:01', '2009-03-07 03:03:01', 'I was notified today that I was not accepted into the CLS program for Intermediate Arabic.  While I am disappointed and frankly a little surprised, it is a competitive scholarship with acceptance rates under 10%.\r\n\r\nTo those of you who were accepted, congratulations.', 'Critical Language Scholarship - Results', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'critical-language-scholarship-results', '', '', '2009-03-06 20:03:01', '2009-03-07 03:03:01', '', 0, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/?p=472', 0, 'post', '', 1),
