009/04/bunnytreeside.png"><img src="http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/bunnytreeside-300x291.png" alt="Profile of the bunny with a very deep octtree." title="bunnytreeside" width="300" height="291" class="size-medium wp-image-528" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nI''m finishing up the implementation, and then I''ll be using it as part of my octtree as a intersection speedup.', 'Octtrees For Space Rasterization', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '525-revision-3', '', '', '2009-04-30 14:50:44', '2009-04-30 21:50:44', '', 525, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2009/04/30/525-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
