 write equations and sometimes table son the graphic itself, and to integrate the caption and legend into the design so that the eye is not required to dart back and fort between textual material and the graphic.\r\n</blockquote>', 'Book Review: Tufte''s "The Visual Display of Quantitative Information"', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '649-autosave', '', '', '2009-10-27 10:20:16', '2009-10-27 17:20:16', '', 649, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2009/10/24/649-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
