SC_0239.NEF''/>\n\nThey cry and scream at one another, but these noises serve as low-priority warnings more than ', 'Monkey Business', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '802-revision', '', '', '2009-12-29 23:39:49', '2009-12-30 06:39:49', '', 802, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2009/12/29/802-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
