 That''s my tech meditation time.', 'Tech Addiction', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '812-revision-2', '', '', '2010-02-07 22:25:09', '2010-02-08 05:25:09', '', 812, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/2010/02/07/812-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(815, 2, '2010-03-08 09:45:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'I would ask of anyone writing a library these days to get rid of compile warnings.  I find it a little disconcerting to see a library compiling with typecasting warnings between pointers.  I won''t name names here, but it is kind of unprofessional.\r\n\r\nSo please, compile with -Wall and fix your warnings.', 'Fix Warnings', 0, '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2010-03-08 09:45:01', '2010-03-08 16:45:01', '', 0, 'http://dan.lecocq.us/wordpress/?p=815', 0, 'post', '', 0),
